{
  "stem": "3757.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So and then came October 15, when they-- in the meantime, a-- Horthy, the governor wanted to get out of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But was too late.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Was afraid that if he goes and parted-- goes away from the Germans, then the Russian will come to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there will be communism.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he-- he denied it, and he-- then he couldn't even do it because the German captured him later.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so it came the October 15, when Szalasi, the main-- how did you call them?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Arrow-- Arrow Cross.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Arrow Cross leader took over the-- the government.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And just on that days, Irene was not there because I sent her home.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It looked a little better, the situation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I sent her home to bring her papers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In the meantime, I talked to this Mrs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Horvat and asked where her son was born.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I know that they were at the-- at the same age.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the-- I went to the, [LAUGHS] yeah, to the city hall.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I said, I am Mrs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Horvat.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I want to have a copy of my son's birthday certificate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they-- they gave it to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And on October 16-- October 15-- this was the first thing what is Szalasi said in a-- in a radio speech, that it's not anymore no Swiss [NON-ENGLISH] pass.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "No Swedish, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It's only Jews, and every Jews has to be killed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And just now, Irene was not there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I was desperate, really.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The next morning, in October 16, I look out of the window.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the whole house is surrounded with German soldiers, up with the weapons to the window.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they yelled, go away from the window in German.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But I understand German, so I know what-- what they say.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
